        <mxCell id="4" value="&lt;b&gt;Risk profile in this 10-commit view&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;C0 is the known-good boundary and is not part of the risk mass. Candidate risks are:&lt;br&gt;C1=0.02, C2=0.10, C3=0.02, C4=0.25, C5=0.02, C6=0.15, C7=0.02, C8=0.95, C9=0.02" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=8;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#d9d9d9;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;spacingLeft=10;spacingRight=10;fontSize=12;" vertex="1" parent="1">
